<p> A Cucumber is a long green fruit, with a subtle, watery taste. </p><br /><br />
<p>My first influence for this food is a Physiological one - Cucumbers are healthy for you as they are full of fiber and vitamins like Vitamin K, and Vitamin C, as well as minerals like Magnesium and Potassium</p><br /><br />
<p>My second influence for this food is an Emotional one - My favourite Non-meal food is cucumber, and when I am stressed, I will sometimes eat cucumber to have less stress</p><br /><br />

- @goto_menu

