<p>Kraft Mac & Cheese, or Kraft Dinner as it is called in Canada, is the flagship product of Kraft Heinz, which is also known for producing Heinz Ketchup. Kraft Heinz itself is a merger of Kraft and Heinz.</p><br /><br />
<p>The first influence for this is an Emotional one - I used to eat Kraft Dinner a lot when I was a kid, which means when I eat kraft dinner now, I get reminded of being a small child </p><br /><br />
<p>The second influence for this is a Media one - When I do see advertisements, sometimes they are for Kraft Dinner, which will sometiems make me want to eat some if I am already in the mood for pasta</p><br /><br />

- @goto_menu

